{
  "chapter": 12,
  "chapter_summary": "龟兹王设宴款待楚留香、姬冰雁、胡铁花及吴氏双侠等人，席间王妃含情打量楚留香后先行告退。龟兹王吐露心事：他被叛臣篡夺王位流亡在外，叛臣从中原重金聘请一流高手行刺。席间驼马夜嘶，姬冰雁外出查看发现石驼已被神秘人王冲带走，心情沉重。龟兹王又透露价值连城的宝石\"极乐之星\"被劫匪夺走，劫匪索要巨额财物交换，龟兹王已答应。楚留香等人答应护送财物前往交换。姬冰雁敏锐分析指出劫匪可能得寸进尺，并暗示龟兹王对\"极乐之星\"另有隐情。突然有人放火引发混乱，姬冰雁识破调虎离山之计，拉楚留香出来观察。楚留香潜回帐篷上方偷窥，发现吴氏双侠露出真面目——吴白云确认四下无人后，吴青天拔剑指向龟兹王，原来吴氏兄弟竟是叛臣派来的卧底刺客。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "高朋满座，家有喜事，人生的乐事，还有什么更甚于此，来!来!来!各位且与小王痛饮三百杯。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_zi_wang_fei",
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王妃",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但望各位尽欢，我体力不支，要先告退了。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 11
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "别的女人你都不妨去打主意，但这是人家的王妃，你可千万不能转糊涂心思。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_qing_tian",
      "speaker_name": "吴青天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那位杜大侠呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他像是很觉无趣，小王虽然再三挽留，他还是连夜要走，最可恼的是，那司徒流星也踪影不见，连人影都找不着了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还有那位王兄呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_bai_yun",
      "speaker_name": "吴白云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这人脾气有些古怪，我再三叫他来，他竟不理我。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 31
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此人不来也罢，他知道小王求才若渴，毛遂自荐而来，却又有些鬼鬼祟祟的，小王就对他不甚相信。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但此刻在这里却都是自己人了，小王有几句心腹之言，想趁着这团喜气说出来，说出之后，更望各位替小王守秘。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_qing_tian",
      "speaker_name": "吴青天",
      "listener": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "text": "王爷只管说，我兄弟绝不是言而无信的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "text": "驸马的好友，怎会背叛王爷?",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正是!正是!小王实在太多虑了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但各位必须体谅小王的处境，小王自从被叛臣所欺，过着被放逐一般的日子，遇事都不能不分外小心了。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小王虽然流浪在外，但心在故国，叛臣们自然也知道此点，是以一心想将小王除之而后快，一年以来，小王已屡次涉险，而且来行刺的并非我龟兹国的武士，而是那些叛臣们自中原找来的刺客。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_qing_tian",
      "speaker_name": "吴青天",
      "listener": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "text": "来的都是些什么人?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "中原侠踪，小王自不熟悉，只知道有一人叫做什么'神刀无敌'，还有一个叫'八臂哪吒'。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_qing_tian",
      "speaker_name": "吴青天",
      "listener": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "text": "王爷只管放心，莫说还有胡兄等三位高人，就凭我兄弟在这里，这些人也休想伤得了王爷毫发。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但据小王所知，那批叛臣最近又自中原重金请来了四五个一流高手，据说其中有一人，剑法之高，简直天下无敌。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_qing_tian",
      "speaker_name": "吴青天",
      "listener": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "text": "王爷可知道他们的名字?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小王只知道其中有四个人在七天前便已来到这附近，还有最厉害的那个人，行踪却诡秘得很。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_bai_yun",
      "speaker_name": "吴白云",
      "listener": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "text": "这消息王爷是从何处得来的?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小王目前虽流浪在外，众叛亲离，但宫中还有几个忠贞之士，在暗中为小王传递消息。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_bai_yun",
      "speaker_name": "吴白云",
      "listener": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "text": "不错，此人藏头露尾，形迹实在可疑。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若是真的刺客卧底，反而更会做出光明磊落之态，以免引人怀疑，面上有些不自然的，反而显得他心中无愧。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "不错，阁下果然目光如炬，小王倒险些错怪好人了，只不过……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 111
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "除此之外，小王还另有件心事。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_qing_tian",
      "speaker_name": "吴青天",
      "listener": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "text": "王爷还有什么心事?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "各位可曾听过'极乐之星'这名字?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_qing_tian",
      "speaker_name": "吴青天",
      "listener": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "text": "在下未曾听过。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那'极乐之星'乃是一粒价值连城的宝石，小王本是委托那彭氏五虎保送的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_bai_yun",
      "speaker_name": "吴白云",
      "listener": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "text": "可是那五虎断门刀的传人么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正是!",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_bai_yun",
      "speaker_name": "吴白云",
      "listener": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "text": "这兄弟五人倒当真可说是武林一流高手，彭家镖局，更是信誉卓着，从未失手，王爷若将东西交给他们，大可高枕无忧，又何必担心?",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 131
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小王也知道他们十分可靠，是以才敢将这天大的责任交给他们，想不到的是，这兄弟五人此刻俱已丧命，'极乐之星'自然也落入别人手中了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_qing_tian",
      "speaker_name": "吴青天",
      "listener": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "text": "这消息当真?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "绝不会假，小王属下已有人看见了他们的尸体。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "text": "王爷可是想要我等去将那'极乐之星'夺回来么?",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小王并非此意。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "text": "王爷的意思是……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不瞒各位，将'极乐之星'劫走的人，方才已传讯与小王。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "text": "传讯的人在哪里?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "据小王属下所报，那人轻功之高，有如鬼魅，将一封信交来之后，立刻就连影子都不见了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "text": "若是如此，那封信呢?",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就在这里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_qing_tian",
      "speaker_name": "吴青天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "单只一枚宝石，能值得了这许多东西么?这人莫非疯了?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他并没有疯。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_qing_tian",
      "speaker_name": "吴青天",
      "listener": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "text": "王爷难道答应了他?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_qing_tian",
      "speaker_name": "吴青天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "其实在下等也可为王爷将那宝石夺回来的。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 177
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小王也并非不信各位没有夺回宝物之力，怕的只是对方知道后，立刻挟宝而逃，天下之大，却叫小王再到哪里去找……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 183
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是以小王宁可牺牲些财物，只要将'极乐之星'得回来也就罢了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 185
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "text": "王爷的意思，是想要我等在三日后的正午，将明珠、白玉送去和他交换么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，小王虽然一心守约，却又怕他们得到这批财物，反而食言背信，各位若肯为小王去走一趟，小王就放心了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "text": "在下等义不容辞，王爷只管放心。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "text": "依在下看来，王爷将东西送去时，他们只怕已不肯交换了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 197
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "为什么?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "text": "他们见到王爷既肯交换，自然也就会想到那'极乐之星'的价值还在这批明珠白玉之上，他们的条件，也就必定会变得更高。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们绝不会这样做的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 207
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "text": "哦?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这'极乐之星'在小王眼中，其价值虽然无法以世俗眼光去估计，但若留在他们的手中，却最多也只不过能值黄金五千两，他们既已平白多得明珠五百粒，玉璧五十面，又怎会再改变主意?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 213
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "text": "王爷却又为何要将这'极乐之星'瞧得特别重呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这自然是个秘密，这秘密普天之下，只有本王一个人知道。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我出去瞧瞧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_bai_yun",
      "speaker_name": "吴白云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "驼马夜嘶，莫非有变?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_bai_yun",
      "speaker_name": "吴白云",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "外面可是发生了什么事?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_wu_bai_yun",
      "text": "没有事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_bai_yun",
      "speaker_name": "吴白云",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "若是无事，驼马为何夜嘶?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_wu_bai_yun",
      "text": "那只不过是因为它们失去了个朋友。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_bai_yun",
      "speaker_name": "吴白云",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "朋友?畜生也有朋友?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_wu_bai_yun",
      "text": "有的人连畜生都不如，却也有朋友，是么?",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "你是说石驼?",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "嗯!",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "他发生了什么事?",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "他走了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "真的走了?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "不但他走了，那王冲也走了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "难道是那王冲将他带走的?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "看来正是如此。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "你不去追?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "不必追。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "为什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "石驼既愿跟他走，其中必有缘故，我们纵然追着，他也必定不会回来，何况我早已答应过他，他要走时，我绝不拦阻。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "这真是个奇怪的人，你真的到现在还不知道他的来历?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "嗯!",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "那王冲来历显然也甚是神秘，你想，这两个人莫非早就认得的么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "text": "在下等酒已足，饭已饱，王爷也该安息了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_zi_wu_shi",
      "speaker_name": "武士",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "火!火!有人放火!",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "莫非又有刺客?各……各位快……快出去瞧瞧。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 289
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_wu_shi",
      "text": "王爷帐外守卫的人呢?",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_zi_wu_shi",
      "speaker_name": "武士",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "小人们知道王爷帐里都是武林豪杰，足可保护王爷的安全。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 309
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好个调虎离山之计。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "你既知道，为何要拉我出来?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我拉你出来，正是好让他们唱戏。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "你是说吴……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你们在留意王妃、公主，我却没有。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "那么现在……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我去找小胡，你去看戏吧!",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这人的心若软些，简直就是世上最可爱的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_bai_yun",
      "speaker_name": "吴白云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "都走远了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": "char_wu_qing_tian",
      "text": "两位千万莫要出去，小王……",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 341
    }
